{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a new FAQ-style education section for Ariya Supplements’ Calm Nights product.
    
    This section should be inspired by the clean expandable accordion style used by premium wellness brands like Moonbrew, AG1, and Grüns.
    
    Section Headline
    Questions About Calm Nights
    
    Supporting Text
    Everything you need to know before your first night.
    
    Layout Requirements
    Mobile-first design.
    Premium wellness aesthetic.
    White background.
    Ariya purple accents.
    Clean typography.
    Large touch-friendly accordion rows.
    Smooth expand/collapse animations.
    One accordion should be expanded by default.
    Plenty of white space.
    Simple and easy to scan.
    Minimalistic luxury design.
    Accordion 1 (Expanded By Default)
    Can Calm Nights Help You?
    
    If any of these sound familiar, Calm Nights was designed for you:
    
    ✓ Your mind won’t stop racing when you lay down
    
    ✓ Stress follows you into bed
    
    ✓ You take more than 30 minutes to fall asleep
    
    ✓ You wake up during the night
    
    ✓ You wake up feeling exhausted
    
    ✓ You want sleep support without melatonin
    
    Accordion 2
    How Does Calm Nights Work?
    
    Calm Nights combines amino acids, botanical extracts, and sleep-support nutrients that help calm a racing mind, support natural sleep pathways, and promote deeper overnight recovery without melatonin.
    
    Accordion 3
    What’s Inside Calm Nights?
    
    Calm Nights contains L-Theanine, L-Tryptophan, Lemon Balm Extract, Chamomile Extract, Tart Cherry Extract, Magnolia Bark Extract, and Vitamin B6.
    
    Every ingredient and dosage is fully disclosed.
    
    No proprietary blends.
    
    Accordion 4
    How To Use
    
    Take 2 capsules 30–60 minutes before bed.
    
    For best results, use consistently as part of a healthy nighttime routine.
    
    Accordion 5
    Quality & Transparency
    
    Every ingredient and dosage is fully disclosed.
    
    Manufactured in an FDA-registered facility and produced following NSF GMP standards.
    
    No proprietary blends.
    
    No hidden doses.
    
    Design Direction
    The first accordion should be expanded by default.
    Use subtle Ariya purple accents for active states.
    Keep the section educational and trustworthy.
    Prioritize readability over decoration.
    Similar visual feel to Moonbrew’s “Can MoonBrew Help You?” section.
    Make users immediately identify with the sleep problems before learning about the formula.
    Goal
    Help visitors self-identify with their sleep struggles, understand how Calm Nights works, and build confidence before purchasing., Center all custom sections across both desktop and mobile.
    Several recently generated sections appear shifted to the left on desktop view.
    Ensure every section uses the same maximum width and horizontal alignment as the rest of the product page.
    All headings, content blocks, comparison sections, statistics sections, and accordion sections should be perfectly centered within the page container.
    Maintain consistent left and right spacing throughout the entire page.
    Do not modify mobile spacing.
    Only correct desktop alignment and container width consistency.
    Match the alignment of the product hero section., this is not centered on the desktop make sure its centered on the desktop, can we make this smaller, make the first tab can calm nights help you not automatically open
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing_mobile }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.accordion_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    border: {{ block.settings.item_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.item_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.item_border_radius }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.item_background }};
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.item_border_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.question_padding_mobile }}px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    gap: 16px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.question_padding_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.question_hover_background }};
  }

  .ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: {{ block.settings.question_color }};
    font-weight: 600;
    flex: 1;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    stroke-width: 2;
  }

  .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    stroke: {{ block.settings.icon_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
  }

  .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-height: 2000px;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.question_padding_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.question_padding_mobile }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 {{ block.settings.question_padding_desktop }}px {{ block.settings.question_padding_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.answer_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.answer_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
{% endstyle %}

<faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-faq-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-faq-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.title != blank or block.settings.subtitle != blank %}
      <div class="ai-faq-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-faq-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.subtitle != blank %}
          <p class="ai-faq-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtitle }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.faq_1_question != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% if block.settings.faq_1_default_open %}active{% endif %}" data-faq-item>
          <button class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-expanded="{% if block.settings.faq_1_default_open %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">
            <span class="ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.faq_1_question }}</span>
            <span class="ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.faq_1_answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.faq_2_question != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-faq-item>
          <button class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.faq_2_question }}</span>
            <span class="ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.faq_2_answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.faq_3_question != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-faq-item>
          <button class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.faq_3_question }}</span>
            <span class="ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.faq_3_answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.faq_4_question != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-faq-item>
          <button class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.faq_4_question }}</span>
            <span class="ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.faq_4_answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.faq_5_question != blank %}
        <div class="ai-faq-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-faq-item>
          <button class="ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ai-faq-question-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.faq_5_question }}</span>
            <span class="ai-faq-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="ai-faq-answer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-faq-answer-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.faq_5_answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class FaqAccordion{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.items = this.querySelectorAll('[data-faq-item]');
        this.setupEventListeners();
      }

      setupEventListeners() {
        this.items.forEach((item) => {
          const button = item.querySelector('.ai-faq-question-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          
          button.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const isActive = item.classList.contains('active');
            
            if (isActive) {
              item.classList.remove('active');
              button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
            } else {
              item.classList.add('active');
              button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
            }
          });
        });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('faq-accordion-{{ ai_gen_id }}', FaqAccordion{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

